	<td bgcolor="#707070" align="left">
		<font face="Verdana,Arial,Helvetica" color="#FFFFFF" size="1">
		<STRONG>Neriak.COM looking for submissions...</STRONG> []
		·· 06-05-2001 at 08:47 AM ·· ^<a href="#top">top</a></font></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
	<td bgcolor="#202050">
	    <font face="Verdana,Arial,Helvetica" size="-2"><br>
		We're once again asking our loyal visitors to offer any content submissions they may have.<p>Guides (trade skill, travel, class, you name it), stories, character histories, humor items -- we're looking for it all!<p>Remember that this is Neriak.COM, and our focus is always on the evil races, so we'll likely only use submissions of interest to those that play evil race and/or class characters.<p>Email any submission you may have to <A HREF="mailto:keeper@neriak.com">keeper@neriak.com</A>.<br>
		<p><font size="1">
		<STRONG>- <a href="mailto:keeper@neriak.com">The Keeper</a></STRONG></font></font></td>
