	    <font face="Verdana,Arial,Helvetica" size="-2"><br>
		It has come to our attention that there is at least one indidivdual out there engaging in what Law Enforcement types like to call COPYRIGHT INFRINGMENT.  Further, this dishonest soul has the AUDACITY to masquerade as our own Gentleman Rogue, Szardos.<p>This will stop.<p>Everything which appears on this site is COPYRIGHTED by the respective author, and further many of the items contain mention of intellectual property held by Verant Interactive or whatever parent company decides to sue the violator =)<p>We want this to be perfectly clear: NOTHING which appears on this site may be used ANYWHERE ELSE by ANYONE except the author of the work involved.<p>Thank you, that is all.<br>
		<p><font size="1">
